      "title": "Apple MacBook Pro A1286 (2012) 15\" Core i7 | 8GB RAM | 500GB HDD | Renewed",
      "description": "Reliable and powerful 15-inch MacBook Pro with Intel Core i7 processor, 8GB RAM, and 500GB storage. Fully tested, refurbished, and ready for daily use.\n\nThe Apple MacBook Pro A1286 (2012) is a classic powerhouse designed for users who need performance, durability, and a premium Apple experience at an affordable price. Featuring a 15-inch display, this device delivers a perfect balance between productivity and entertainment.\n\nPowered by an Intel Core i7 processor, it ensures smooth multitasking, whether you're working on documents, browsing, or handling moderate creative tasks. The 8GB RAM allows efficient performance across multiple applications, while the 500GB HDD provides ample storage for files, media, and software.\n\nThis unit is professionally refurbished and tested, ensuring it functions perfectly. It may show minor cosmetic signs of previous use, but performance is fully reliable.\n\nIdeal for:\n\u2714 Office work\n\u2714 Students\n\u2714 Online business & browsing\n\u2714 Media consumption\n\nA great choice for anyone looking for a budget-friendly Apple MacBook Pro with strong performance.\n\nKey Features:\n- \ud83d\udcbb 15-inch LED-backlit display\n- \u26a1 Intel Core i7 processor\n- \ud83e\udde0 8GB RAM for smooth multitasking\n- \ud83d\udcbe 500GB HDD storage\n- \ud83d\udd0b Good battery backup (varies with usage)\n- \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Fully tested & refurbished\n- \ud83c\udfaf Durable aluminum unibody design\n- \ud83c\udf4e macOS compatible",
      "price": 550,
      "originalPrice": 890,
