      "title": "Apple (Refurbished) iPhone 15 Pro Max, 1TB, Natural Titanium - Dual eSIM (US Version)",
      "description": "Refurbished Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max 1TB in Natural Titanium with A17 Pro chip, 6.7-inch display, pro camera system, and massive storage. Dual eSIM US version.\n\nGet maximum storage and performance with the refurbished iPhone 15 Pro Max 1TB in Natural Titanium. Powered by the A17 Pro chip, this flagship device offers ultra-smooth performance, a stunning 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display, and a powerful 48MP pro camera system. The 1TB storage is ideal for professionals, content creators, and heavy users who need space for 4K videos, apps, and files. This US version supports Dual eSIM and is fully tested for quality and reliability.\n\nKey Features:\n- A17 Pro chip for ultra-fast performance\n- 6.7-inch Super Retina XDR display\n- 1TB massive internal storage\n- 48MP professional camera system\n- Natural Titanium premium finish\n- Dual eSIM (US Version)\n- Face ID security\n- 5G connectivity\n- Refurbished and quality tested\n- Perfect for creators and heavy users",
